[center][u]T67_Coffins[/u]

version 1.0

Author : Tony67


[u]Description :[/u]

Copy the meshes in Skyrim/Data/meshes
Copy the textures in Skyrim/Data/meshes

In the Creation Kit, right-click in Statics, click New, then Edit and choose your mesh. Name it and place it anywhere you want in your cell.

Coming Soon : Dwemer Style and Rock Style

[u]Tools Used :[/u]

Nifskope 1.1.0 RC7
GIMP 2.6.12


[u]Credits :[/u]

Bethesda for the vanilla meshes.
